        cases 08, 09) - this party tests the polymorphic Organization
        branch on the GENERAL INQUIRY flow's In Progress case; party
        07 (Org Respondent on case 08) tests the same on the Complaint
        flow's In Progress case. Together these two Organization rows
        on the same lifecycle phase (In Progress) but different flow
        paths prove the Organization branch works on both flows.
