          party_type  - Choice (Person | Organization, mandatory)
          person      - Reference -> sys_user (conditional: required
                        if party_type=Person)
          organization- Reference -> core_company (conditional: required
                        if party_type=Organization)
          role_label  - String(100) (mandatory; example values
                        Requester, Respondent, Witness)

      With party_type=Organization, the conditional UI Policy at
      ../../ui_policy/x_[scope]_case_party_conditional_fields.xml
      activates the Organization branch:
          - Show + require <organization> field (populated below with
            "Synthetic Org Alpha")
          - Hide <person> field (left empty below; the empty <person/>
            element preserves the dictionary entry's existence while
            signaling no value)

      Case 03 is in In Progress status on the General Inquiry flow per
      ../cases/x_[scope]_case_demo_03.xml. The case was filed by an
      external requester submitting a General Inquiry about Synthetic
